description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Urban Scenery of Tokyo
-Rainbow Bridge and Fireworks
-Chidorigafuchi in full bloom
-Mitake Valley in autumn leaves
-Okutama Valley in autumn leaves
-Fan Pond in Minamijima island
-Sakaiura Beach, Chichijima island
-Mimamizaki, Hahajima island
-Nezire Falls, Unazawa Valley
-Tomari Beach, Shikinejima island
name: Tokyo - Most beautiful places in Japan -
